node.text:
Cross-Country MTB racing in Snowshoe 🇺🇸 always delivers a show to remember 🔥. 

Two years ago @larsrace snatched victory from his teammate @nschurter with less than quarter of the lap to go & claimed his first elite World Cup win. 

Make sure you join us on Red Bull TV today & watch all the action LIVE 👉 bio.

⏰: Women's race 12.00pm EDT / 5.00pm BST / 6.00pm CEST

⏰: Men's race 2.30pm EDT / 7.30pm BST / 8.30pm CEST

#bike #mtb #bikelife #crosscountrymtb #xco

node.text:
@valihoell racing season might have not started as she pictured, but it sure ended way beyond her wildest dreams 🔥. Her stellar performances during the season finale in Snowshoe 🇺🇸 brought her:

👉 First ever Downhill World Cup elite win 🥇
👉 Second ever Downhill World Cup elite win 🥇
👉  2021 UCI Mountain Bike Downhill World Cup Overall Winner title 🏆.

Watch the full replay on Red Bull TV 👉 bio.

#bike #mtb #bikelife #downhillmtb #downhill

node.text:
We couldn't have asked for a more dramatic ending to this epic season of racing! 🔥
Snowshoe is in the books and we wanna take a second to thank everyone involved in this insane two-wheeled world! Riders, Mechanics, Marshalls, Technicians... and most importantly: YOU - THE FANS! This was amazing. 🙏💯
 
We can't wait to see you all back in 2022 for more of this! 🤘

Cross-Country MTB racing in Snowshoe 🇺🇸 always delivers a show to remember 🔥. 

Two years ago @larsrace snatched victory from his teammate @nschurter with less than quarter of the lap to go & claimed his first elite World Cup win. 

Make sure you join us on Red Bull TV today & watch all the action LIVE 👉 bio.

⏰: Women's race 12.00pm EDT / 5.00pm BST / 6.00pm CEST

⏰: Men's race 2.30pm EDT / 7.30pm BST / 8.30pm CEST
